51 + /**

53 +  * <ul>

68 +                     Swagger.class);

94 +                 if (!"code".equals(request.getForm().getFirst("response_type"))) {
95 +                     return error(redirectUri, "unsupported_response_type", state);
96 +                 }

103 +                     userCodes.put(code, json(object(field("user", user), field("redirect_uri", redirectUri))));
104 +                     return code(redirectUri, code, state);

128 +         });

171 +                 return newResultPromise(new Response(OK).setEntity(json(object(
172 +                         field("access_token", token),

176 +
177 +             private Promise<Response, NeverThrowsException> error(String error) {

181 +         router.addRoute(requestUriMatcher(EQUALS, "api"), new Handler() {
182 +             public Promise<Response, NeverThrowsException> handle(Context context, Request request) {
183 +                 if (!"GET".equals(request.getMethod())) {
184 +                     return newResultPromise(new Response(METHOD_NOT_ALLOWED));
185 +                 }
186 +                 String authValue = getAuthorizationHeader(request);
187 +                 if (authValue != null && authValue.startsWith("Bearer ")) {

190 +                         return newResultPromise(new Response(OK).setEntity(json(object(field("user", user)))));
191 +                     }
192 +                 }
193 +                 return newResultPromise(new Response(Status.UNAUTHORIZED));
